{"tid":2218233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢排係唔係太多冷嘲熱諷?","createTime":"2020-09-26T05:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T05:52:05.000Z","uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"60ef8043a4f340d893b77677c6c38206136d203d","tid":2218233,"uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"潘曉穎母親警告陳同佳 10月23日是你的最後期限<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2217948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2217948</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n嚇死人咩，咁多人幫陳同佳講好說話，我知實有人玩膠，甚至有藍絲露出本性，各位可唔可以少啲冷嘲熱諷呢? <br />\n<br />\n你話敵人可以冷嘲熱諷，咁呢件事上面我哋應該支持個老母先啱㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時事討論明明好適合理性分析，但係買少見少。"},{"pid":"9d5c368bdc1cb5745330d95d924f44971b719cd2","tid":2218233,"uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係大家鐘意依家咁多啲"},{"pid":"09bb9be31e8d8c766109617570314aa821835e9d","tid":2218233,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:50:50.000Z","msg":"香港人反既係港共用呢件事借D易將香港中共化, 同埋之後引起既一切<br />\n佢兩個本身點, 係另一回事"},{"pid":"aad794927247fad601b84105b7bca56f1532ec30","tid":2218233,"uid":10125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:52:05.000Z","msg":"可憐之人必有可恨之處 好似係"}]}